registry.title: IANA-PRINTER-MIB
registry.description:
This MIB module defines a set of printing-related TEXTUAL-CONVENTIONs for use in Printer MIB , Finisher MIB , and other MIBs which need to specify printing mechanism details.
Any additions or changes to the contents of this MIB module require either publication of an RFC, or Designated Expert Review as defined in , Guidelines for Writing an IANA Considerations Section in RFCs. The Designated Expert will be selected by the IESG Area Director(s) of the Applications Area.
